牛屎飛同義士一路<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">文宣只可針對黑狗，勿再屌白衫</span></span>"},{"pid":"4460a27bb9a04ffe2eda49fba23325bf27965e4c","tid":1346380,"uid":203743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T23:05:05.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">打狗呀屌你老母<br />\n咪做on9仔被共狗消耗你專心</span></span>"}]}